1. Clone the linux tree
	git clone git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git

2. Copy the current kernel configuration file to new linux folder
	cd linux
	cp /boot/config-`uname -r`* .config

3. Change CONFIG_LOCALVERSION_AUTO=y i .config file

4. Build the kernelOptional:

	make localmodconfig

5. Install the kernel
	sudo make modules_install install

6. Reboot


